 Virgin Atlantic announced it would allow each passenger one Facebook login for free so they can post an update from 35,000 ft.
The #SkyhighSelfie is one of the unusual extras being offered on the airline 's Dreamliner 787 routes , alongside mood lighting to help with jetlag , windows that can be darkened with a touch of a button and full windows in the toilets .
Other features include full-length mirrors in the cabin .